                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>@Compendium[pf2e.bestiary-ability-glossary-srd.Aura]{Aura} 5 feet.</p>\n<p>The scented candle homunculus's fragrance of lavender is overwhelmingly intense. Any creature other than the homunculus's master who enters the aura must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:15] save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is temporarily immune to the homunculus's aura for 24 hours.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stupefied]{Stupefied 1} for 1 round and sickened 1.</p>"
